Package: v2v
Title: Companion Package for 'From Vibes to Variables'
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alex P.", "Leith", , "aleith@siue.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7330-2153"))
Description: Companion R package for the open educational resource
    'From Vibes to Variables: A Field Guide to Open Media Science' by
    Alex P. Leith. Ships a stratified subset of a 2018 Twitch chat and
    stream dataset, scaffolding functions for student portfolios, and
    pedagogical helpers for sampling, intercoder reliability, timestamp
    conversion, and joining the chat and stream tables. Used in SIUE
    MC-451 (Research Methods) and MC-501 (Graduate).
